# Privacy Policy
 
**FlexWord — Daily FlexWord, FlexPlay, and FlexArena**
Operated by TheForklift.dev LLC
Effective date: April 19, 2026
 
## The short version
 
FlexWord is a free game on Reddit. We store your gameplay data (guesses, scores, settings) using Reddit's built-in storage so the game works. We don't collect your email, your name, or any personal information beyond what Reddit already provides through the Devvit platform. We don't sell data. We don't run ads.
 
## What data FlexWord stores
 
FlexWord uses Redis storage provided by the Devvit platform to store:
 
* Your game state (current puzzle progress, guesses made, scores)
* Your game settings and preferences (selected difficulty, word length, guess count)
* FlexArena challenge data (challenge invitations, results, and opponent usernames as provided by Reddit)
* Aggregate, non-identifying gameplay statistics used to improve word difficulty calibration
This data is tied to your Reddit user ID as provided by the Devvit platform. We do not collect or store your Reddit password, email address, or any information beyond what Devvit makes available to installed apps.
 
## Network requests
 
FlexWord may make HTTP requests to external APIs to retrieve word definitions. These requests contain only the word being looked up. They do not include your Reddit username, user ID, or any other identifying information.
 
## What we don't do
 
* We don't sell or share your data with third parties
* We don't serve ads
* We don't track you across Reddit or the web
* We don't collect data from minors knowingly (FlexWord has no age gate, but collects no personal information beyond Reddit-provided user IDs)
## Where data lives
 
All gameplay data is stored through Reddit's Devvit platform infrastructure. TheForklift.dev LLC does not operate separate servers or databases for user data. Data retention and infrastructure security are governed by Reddit's own policies.
 
## Data deletion
 
Because FlexWord data is stored through Reddit's Devvit platform, your data is associated with your Reddit account. If you want your FlexWord data removed, contact us at r/FlexWord and we will delete your stored game data. Uninstalling or leaving the r/FlexWord community does not automatically delete stored data.
 
## Changes to this policy
 
We may update this policy. Changes will be announced at r/FlexWord. Continued use of FlexWord after changes means you accept the updated policy.
 
## Contact
 
Questions about this privacy policy can be directed to r/FlexWord or to TheForklift.dev LLC through the contact information listed at theforklift.dev.
 
